# 🎓 A.O.P.E Student Portal (Demo Project)

This is a simple web-based student portal built for **Adeseun Ogundoyin Polytechnic, Eruwa** as a school project.

---

## 📌 Features

- 🔐 Student Login System (Matric Number + Password)
- ⏳ 15-Second Loading Animation after login
- 🏠 Student Dashboard
- 👤 Profile Page
- 📚 Courses Page
- 📊 Results Page
- 📅 Timetable
- 💳 Payment Section (School Fees, SIWES, CBT)
- 🧾 Receipt Generator (Popup + Print option)
- 🟢 Second Semester Active Status
- 📢 Animated Notice Board

